Actor Walker and driver Roger Rodas died on November 30 when their Porsche
Carrera GT hit a light pole and tree and caught fire in the Los Angeles suburb
of Santa Clarita.

Prosecutors claim Witty and Janow stole a roof panel from the wrecked
Porsche as it was being towed away.

Witty was caught on video stealing the T-top roof of the Porsche right off the tow truck and afterwards he even bragged about the heist by posting pics of the stolen wreckage on Instagram.

Witty is free on bail and Janow is expected to surrender on Tuesday. It wasn't immediately clear whether they had obtained lawyers.

